      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Solid contest with plenty of last start winners. INFANT WARRIOR (1) justified the short price when she held off the challengers to get the job done over this trip at Hawkesbury in good style. Can handle the 2kg weight rise and prove hard to stop. THE NETBALL QUEEN (2) on the ten-day back-up when she sped to the front for a blistering 3.5 len victory over 1000m at Wyong. Will go quickly again from the inside draw in what shapes as a competitive contest. MYSTIC AIR (7) beat inferior opposition on debut in the small field over 1000m at Orange a month ago. Has further upside with top-four prospects. VANTANTE (6) failed to stretch out in the heavy (9) going with a fading sixth over 1000m at Kembla Grange. Can stalk the good tempo and improve quickly.",
